39:  * <p>
40:  * An Over-The-Counter (OTC) trade in an {@link FxVanillaOption}.
41:  * <p>
42:  * An FX option is a financial instrument that provides an option based on the future value of
43:  * a foreign exchange. The option is European, exercised only on the exercise date.
44:  */
